description.en: "The Syllabus Ontology" is an ontology that allows to represent information of academic content of Higher Education Institutions (HEI) of Ecuador.
description.es: La Ontología de Sílabos es una ontología que permite representar  información de contenidos académicos de carrera (Sílabos) de Instituciones de Educación Superior (IES) del Ecuador.

comments.en: The Academic Institution Internal Structure Ontology (AIISO) provides classes and properties to describe the internal organizational structure of an academic institution. AIISO is designed to work in partnership with Participation (http://purl.org/vocab/participation/schema), FOAF (http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/) and aiiso-roles (http://purl.org/vocab/aiiso-roles/schema) to describe the roles that people play within an institution.
